sentences: Tomislav Zografski was a Macedonian composer (1934–2000) and music pedagogue who also wrote music for film and television.
Zografski was born in Veles, Kingdom of Yugoslavia (now Macedonia) on 29 March 1934.
Zografski was born in Veles, Kingdom of Yugoslavia (now Macedonia) on 29 March 1934.
In 1967 he became professor at the Faculty of Music, Ss.
